&s;hort continuance. A circum&s;tance oc|curred
that renewed the mi&s;ery, which
can now never quit me but in the grave,
to which I look with no fearful appre|hen&s;ion,
but as a refuge from calamity,
tru&s;ting that the power who has &s;een
