of my devotion, and the too
<PB N="41" REF="45">
frequent wandering of my thoughts to
the objects once &s;o dear to me."</P>
<P>As &s;he &s;poke &s;he rai&s;ed her eyes,
which beamed with truth and meek a&s;|&s;urance,
to heaven; and the fine devo|tional
